        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>This polished crystal sphere enhances scrying magic. Any visual information received through a spell with the scrying trait that was cast by the <em>crystal ball</em> appears within the sphere, and any auditory information sounds out from the surface of the sphere. When you cast a <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"r784cIz17eWujtQj\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Scrying</a> spell by any other means while holding the sphere, you can relay any information you receive in the same way, allowing others to see or hear the target.</p>\n<p>The base version of a <em>crystal ball</em> is a sphere of clear quartz, but other versions are made of different stones.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> 1 minute (command, envision, Interact)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The <em>crystal ball</em> casts <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"zvKWclOZ7A53DObE\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Clairvoyance</a> to your specifications.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> 10 minutes (command, envision, Interact)</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> twice per day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The <em>crystal ball</em> casts a DC 39 <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"r784cIz17eWujtQj\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Scrying</a> spell to your specifications, and you gain the benefits of <a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"pf2e.spells-srd\" data-id=\"HqTI6wRrck1YXp3F\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Telepathy</a> on the target.</p>"
